### Create a user
POST http://localhost:5239/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer valid-token

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com"
}

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:5239/api/users
Authorization: Bearer valid-token

### Get a user by ID
GET http://localhost:5239/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer valid-token

### Update a user
PUT http://localhost:5239/api/users/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer valid-token

{
  "id": 2,
  "name": "Dewb Smith",
  "email": "johnsmith@example.com"
}

### Delete a user
DELETE http://localhost:5239/api/users/3
Authorization: Bearer valid-token

